        {
            "title": "小米據報成立晶片平台部 前高通主管秦牧雲任負責人",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">《新浪科技》引述小米(01810)日前的內部宣布，指出集團在手機部門下成立晶片平台部，由前高通主管秦牧雲任負責人。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道指，秦牧雲將向產品部總經理李俊報告。近期有消息指出，小米15S Pro將首度搭載小米自研SoC晶片登場。日前，小米聯合創辦人、副董事長林斌也在微博上回覆網友時首次確認了小米15S Pro新機的存在，但這款新機的具體規格，仍待小米官方確認。 </p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14856870-%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e6%88%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%99%b6%e7%89%87%e5%b9%b3%e5%8f%b0%e9%83%a8-%e5%89%8d%e9%ab%98%e9%80%9a%e4%b8%bb%e7%ae%a1%e7%a7%a6%e7%89%a7%e9%9b%b2%e4%bb%bb%e8%b2%a0%e8%b2%ac",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230703-123043__source-web_01810-3_source-web_-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 17:15:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "據報中國要求內地航空公司暫緩接收波音飛機",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中美關稅戰爭持不下，《彭博》引述消息人士指，中國已要求內地航空公司暫緩接收等待交付的波音飛機。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/10/20240801_FI_source-ap_US_China-704.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">除了暫時不要接收波音飛機外，報道指中國亦要求內地航空公司停止從美國公司購買飛機相關零件與設備。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">報道指，內地作出上述決定，主要是考慮到在新關稅措施下，現時接收波音這家美國企業生產的飛機，成本勢大幅增加，中國有關部門正就此研究支援方案。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14856812-%e6%93%9a%e5%a0%b1%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%a6%81%e6%b1%82%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e8%88%aa%e7%a9%ba%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e6%9a%ab%e7%b7%a9%e6%8e%a5%e6%94%b6%e6%b3%a2%e9%9f%b3%e9%a3%9b%e6%a9%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240110_FI_source-ap_Boeing.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 17:05:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "華潤電力上月售電量按年升2.5% 首季增1.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華潤電力(00836)公布，今年3月份售電量達1702.28萬兆瓦時，按年增2.5%；首季累計售電量5011.53萬兆瓦時，按年升1.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤電力官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230719_FI_source-web_00836-logo.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤電力官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230719_FI_source-web_00836-logo.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤電力官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">單計集團隂屬風電場，上月售電量494.16萬兆瓦時，按年升7.1%；首季累計售電量1299.74萬兆瓦時，按年升9.2%。光伏電站上月售電量65.14萬兆瓦時，按年增長14.1%；首季累計售電量達173.14萬兆瓦時，按年提升33.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14856755-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e9%9b%bb%e5%8a%9b%e4%b8%8a%e6%9c%88%e5%94%ae%e9%9b%bb%e9%87%8f%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%872-5-%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%a2%9e1-7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20230719_FI_source-web_00836.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-15 16:45:34",
